productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Isabela has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks monochromatic.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
My co-worker Kazuo has one of these. He says it looks transparent.
My co-worker Cato has one of these. He says it looks sopping.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This Soft keeps them away.
